== Overview ==

The wordmorph app finds the minimum number of changes required to transform one word into another, changing only one letter at a time with the restriction that the intermediates are also english words.

Formally, the hamming distance on the set of english words.

Example:
            <a href="http://www.dictionary.com/browse/free">free</a> ->
            <a href="http://www.dictionary.com/browse/bree"><em>b</em>ree</a> ->
            <a href="http://www.dictionary.com/browse/bren">bre<em>n</em></a> ->
            <a href="http://www.dictionary.com/browse/been">b<em>e</em>en</a> ->
            <a href="http://www.dictionary.com/browse/beer">bee<em>r</em></a> ->

